{"tid":147145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"型男為愛犬　轉行煮狗糧","createTime":"2017-03-07T15:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T02:46:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a0d0c36d78eb2e9a630f57fd1b92a9b3060388","tid":147145,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170307/org/1488808861_5dad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170307%2Forg%2F1488808861_5dad.jpg&h=00d79d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/06/3292571/20170307_Vvvsub404_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F3292571%2F20170307_Vvvsub404_clean_w.mp4&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3ePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=e85fc975\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/06/3292571/20170307_Vvvsub404_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe02p.jpg&h=ddeed521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Alexis自言不太懂廚藝，只是因為關注狗隻健康才開始學煮狗糧。 <br />\n <br />\n很多人說養狗後性格會改變，其實可能連未來也會改變，就如型男鄺志華（Alexis），當初沒想過養八哥狗，最後卻因愛犬毅然轉行，日日煮健康狗糧。 <br />\n <br />\nAlexis在愛護動物協會遇上八哥Megan後一見鍾情，三年後再領養Phoebe及Tina一對八哥，他認為八哥安靜得來偶爾會玩到癲，喜歡撒嬌，體形細小，適合城市人飼養。他在傳媒行業工作多年，年半前辭職，那時發現Phoebe喉嚨位置長了癌腫瘤，兩個月後過身，於是他開始研究狗生癌會否受飲食習慣影響。搜尋相關資料後，發現消委會曾指本港市面約兩成狗糧含致癌物黃曲霉毒素，便開始煮食物給狗吃。至去年，有澳洲動物營養師幫他設計狗餐單，三個月前正式成立新鮮手工狗糧品牌「Dogalicious」。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe03p.jpg&h=ca95c162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Tina一天吃兩餐，每次食用約100克鮮狗糧。不消五分鐘便狼吞虎嚥吃完，相信新鮮狗糧比乾糧吸引得多。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe08pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe08pzok.jpg&h=129be3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 手工製新鮮狗糧主要材料有龍脷柳、沙甸魚、雞肉、紅蘿蔔、番薯、芥蘭、菜心、豆角、藍莓及雞蛋等，每款均計算所提供能量、蛋白、脂肪及醣類，狗狗便可食得更健康。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe07pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe07pzok.jpg&h=600f7cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 手工製新鮮狗糧每天入袋後即真空處理，放進雪櫃可保存八天，每個餐單份量為一星期，會根據狗隻體重計算所需份量。 <br />\n <br />\n<strong>新鮮狗糧　加飯當午餐</strong><br />\n一般由雞肉壓縮成深啡色的狗乾糧，當中可能加入了大量雜質及化學物質，Alexis：「人每天都吃午餐肉也無益，其實狗也一樣，有時煮新鮮狗糧時太肚餓，我也會加點飯直接當午餐吃。」因為八哥皮膚易敏感，9歲的Tina開始吃魚肉口味餐單，吃畢減重且毛色亮澤，比一般同齡的狗更少白髮。他看過外國報道揭發有狗糧品牌用動物屍體混入狗糧，甚至有某知名狗糧品牌即使標示用新鮮雞肉，裏面也測出有狗肉DNA，所以如非必要（如醫生處方糧），他都不建議狗吃乾糧，假如大家沒時間煮，大可烚雞肉放入冰箱，吃前用熱水浸熱，總比一世只吃乾糧好。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe04pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe04pzok.jpg&h=1791ae34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 牛肉口味含牛肉及牛肝，鐵質豐富。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe05pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe05pzok.jpg&h=8c34e25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 魚肉口味有龍脷柳和沙甸魚，含豐富鈣質和Omega3，還加入屬超級食物的藜麥。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe06pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe06pzok.jpg&h=fbaa30ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 雞肉口味額外添加藍莓，以加強護眼效果。 <br />\n <br />\n<strong>不含調味料　加蛋殼添鈣質</strong><br />\n新鮮烹調的狗糧有魚、雞及牛三款口味，三種肉類都用焗爐烤熟，菜則蒸熟以保存營養，不下任何調味料，加入飯和藜麥，並混入切碎的紅蘿蔔、番薯、芥蘭或菜心幫助消化。Alexis：「也會將蛋殼壓碎混入狗糧，因蛋殼含天然鈣質，對骨骼和牙齒有益，另外添加含Omega3及維他命E的動物亞麻籽油，對狗的腸胃、心臟及皮毛也有幫助。」如果家中狗狗要減肥或皮膚敏感，便可試較低卡路里的魚肉餐。訪問完畢後，我試吃了一粒狗乾糧，沒味道之餘還有股魚糧怪味，留在口中久久不散，家中狗狗不太愛吃狗乾糧，其實不無原因。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe11p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe11p.jpg&h=0ba182da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Alexis就算忙於工作，也會盡量花時間陪Tina，每天早晚散步一次。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe12p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe12p.jpg&h=322cbe1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 他養的三隻八哥Phoebe（前）、Megan（後）及Tina。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe13p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe13p.jpg&h=2557aa5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 一周前Alexis聯同小店kapok及保護遺棄動物組織LAP合辦八哥跑步比賽，為遺棄動物籌款及呼籲領養，雖然賽道只長十米，當天仍吸引近百人觀戰。有些八哥怒奔到終點，有些則散步，場面有趣。"},{"pid":"962eed8e327df708571340f1e4285d6330cc88fb","tid":147145,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170307/large/07fe09p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170307%2Flarge%2F07fe09p.jpg&h=5fbb4bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 他將肉切成小粒，方便牠們咀嚼和消化。 <br />\n <br />\n<strong>易皮膚敏感忌攝取</strong><br />\n1.蛋白質，肉類可能含令狗過敏的蛋白質。<br />\n2.麩質，很多穀類如麵包也有這類致敏原。<br />\n3.高調味食物。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nfacebook：Dogalicious<br />\n收費：首星期免費，其後因應狗隻體重及不同份量收費，小型狗如8至10公斤約每周$200。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n註：註冊獸醫黎昌生指，狗狗只吃乾糧其實並不會直接影響健康，部份狗糧品牌與大學進行科研，以便為狗狗提供更全面的營養。其實狗狗的飲食習慣亦建基於主人的生活習慣，能花時間煮新鮮糧食當然好，不過新鮮食材有季節性，加上香港人生活忙碌，乾糧價錢較便宜、儲存方便，便成為都市生活的狗狗主要糧食。那究竟濕糧還是乾糧比較好？濕糧水份多，對狗狗來說較美味，不過狗狗平日多吃乾糧的話，醫生亦建議吃後多飲水便可以。"},{"pid":"b5ec10c3549a033b086eeee80e963d3800993e4f","tid":147145,"uid":38102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"八哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b5232a8465b672e5142215af8189918b17b1a1","tid":147145,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"愛錫動物的人是最美的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237833f5db7f73969dbc8b170b955c1a3dc84013","tid":147145,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"八哥個樣好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39c3fca9a616d8529e64ab7598d984969d22132","tid":147145,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img s